snippet.title: Celebrities Who Treat Their Significant Others Like Trash
snippet.description:
When you’re a celebrity in a high-profile relationship, it can be hard to live your life like a regular person; all eyes are on you and your significant other at all times. If you do something incredibly sweet for your partner, you’ll quickly endear yourself to the public and win fans, but if you treat them like trash, it is going to get out. It might come out right away, or it might take years, but eventually people will find out what kind of partner you really are, and it is going to do a number on your career. Let’s take a look at some celebrities who treated their significant others like trash.
